reviewText: Great movie, and Mike Pfaff was fantastic!
One of the best movies I've ever seen. Go watch it now you will not be disapointed.

This movie is amazing!! Kept me on the edge of my seat the entire time. I keep recommending this film to all of my friends for movie nights. Mike Pfaff does an amazing job in this film (first saw him on Days of our Lives recently). Definitely one to own!
My name is Sal and this movie was bangin bruh. I love Mike Pfaff, he's the man. My boys are going to dress up as him for halloween this year! Keep up the good work guys!

This movie was truly thrilling and suspenseful with the movie being told from 2 perspectives. Michael (Mike Pfaff) being the loving husband that deals with the agony of having his wife disappear for mysterious reasons, and having him struggle to find out his wife's secret for her disappearance leaves the audience on the edge of her seat while learning about his wife's escape from the merciless mob lead by Sal Rendino and Adoni Maropis.

What an amazing film! It kept me on the edge of my seat the whole time, I don't think I have ever seen another movie like this one before. I will recommend this movie to everyone especially because Mike Pfaff is amazing!!!
Hi my name is Brook!  I really enjoyed this movie, it was really good for a Friday night with the boys! Mike Pfaff is a tremendous actor!!
looks like a great film!

Saw Mike Pfaff in The Librarians and he was amazing! He does a great job as the lead character in this and you should go check out some of the other productions he is in!! Great movie and I would absolutely recommend this to a friend.
Wow what a great movie! Kept my attention the entire time-E. Duer

Amazing!! Best actor ever!!! Super talented. Love love loved it!!!!!

Lazarus Rising was a fantastic movie! The 2015 crime movie kept you on the edge of your seat! I would recommend this to everyone I know!

This movie did not work for me at any level.

I just saw this movie and liked it so much I had to buy it.  First movie I have purchased in 3 years.  Well done.  Acting very impressive for such a low-budget film.  In particular, Mike Pfaff and C. Thomas Howell excelled.  I have followed Mike Pfaff in other projects - The Librarians and as a neighbor in Two Broke Girls.  I love what he is doing.  Nice work by all.
Excellent movie and price !

In Lazarus Rising, Mike Pfaff once again shows us his versatility as an actor.  His commitment to his craft, doing some of his own stunts, and ability to play roles with an inner sense of the character should really offer - at least some insight - to what Pfaff adds to the discipline of method acting.  The great method actors; Pacino, DeNiro, etc may have the opportunity, dare I say, to learn something from Pfaff's sense of honesty and purity to acting.  Pfaff "gives himself" to his character, saving Emma at all costs, with no compromise.

Awesome action film with a lot of unexpected twists and turns that keep you guessing.  It mixes politics and crime, I guess they are really one in the same. Acting is convincing. For me it is a keeper.
An underdog of a movie, but none the less a great one. The plot was surprisingly entertaining and everyone did a great job but specifically Mike Pfatt had a great performance.

Mike plaff killed it. Let this man become the new superman to replace Henry cavill.

Mike Paff was incredible in this film! Just recently saw him in Fields of Valor, incredible actor and this film was riviting and kept me entertained the whole time! Highly recommended!

I can't say enough positive things about this film!!!!! The lead character did an incredible job. I just showed it to my friends when they slept over and they totally loved it as well. It is a must see!!!!

Great movie surprised it isn't more popular. Not only did this movie feature an interesting plot but it also featured an amazing cast, in particular Mike Pfaff. I highly would recommend this movie to all my friends!
